OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FSeveral areas of England are at risk
OL,8,Fof entering their second drought in
OL,9,Ftwo years after persistent heatwaves
OL,10,Fand a lack of rain put pressure on the
OL,11,Fwater supply.
OL,13,FAccording to the National Drought
OL,14,FGroup, parts of southern, central and
OL,15,Feastern England are moving closer to a
OL,16,Fdrought.
OL,18,FThe UK has been through three
OL,19,Fheatwaves already this year, and
OL,20,Fforecasters have said another cannot
OL,21,Fbe ruled out before the end of summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
