OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784663291
OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FThe National Drought Group said the
OL,8,FJuly heatwave led to demand for water
OL,9,Fsoaring up to 30% on the hottest days.
OL,11,FRainfall totals for the month of July
OL,12,Fto date ranged from 9% of the long-
OL,13,Fterm average in north-west England to
OL,14,Fnothing in east and south-east
OL,15,FEngland, the Met Office said.
OL,17,FOverall England has seen just 3% of
OL,18,Fits normal rainfall in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
