OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FAs a result, eight areas across
OL,8,FEngland have been declared to be in
OL,9,Fprolonged dry weather ` the stage
OL,10,Fbefore drought.
OL,12,FMuch of England experienced a drought
OL,13,Flast year after one of the driest
OL,14,Fsprings on record left reservoirs
OL,15,Facross the country almost empty.
OL,17,FWhere have hosepipe bans been declared?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
