OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784663291
OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FThe Thames Water region received only
OL,8,F40% of average rainfall this spring,
OL,9,Ffollowed by periods of exceptionally
OL,10,Fhot weather, the firm said.
OL,12,FBans are also in place for Southern
OL,13,FWater customers in Hampshire and the
OL,14,FIsle of Wight, Cambridge Water
OL,15,Fcustomers, Affinity Water customers in
OL,16,FBedfordshire, Berkshire,
OL,17,FBuckinghamshire, Essex, Hertfordshire,
OL,18,FSurrey and parts of London, and
OL,19,FAnglian Water customers in the East of
OL,20,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
