OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FOn Monday, South East Water also
OL,8,Fannounced that 2.4 million customers
OL,9,Fwill be affected by temporary
OL,10,Frestrictions in Sussex, Surrey,
OL,11,FHampshire and Berkshire from Saturday,
OL,12,Fcoming on top of a ban it already put
OL,13,Fin place for areas of Kent.
OL,15,FSevern Trent, Essex and Suffolk Water,
OL,16,FWessex Water and Portsmouth Water have
OL,17,Falso urged customers to use water
OL,18,Fwisely amid the heatwave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
