OL,3,CThe areas of England at risk of
OL,4,Cdrought ` and where hosepipe bans are
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FIn total, around 23 million people in
OL,8,FEngland are already under hosepipe
OL,9,Fbans.
OL,11,FThe National Drought Group also said
OL,12,Fsome farmers are opting to harvest
OL,13,Fearly to save their crops but warned
OL,14,Fthis would result in lower yields.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
